00:14:43.280 --> 00:14:44.980
<font color="#138ce9">ABUELITA ELENA:</font> In the courtyard. <i>mijos.</i>

266
00:14:44.990 --> 00:14:46.150
<font color="#138ce9">PAPA:</font> You want it
down by the kitchen?

