00:16:40.110 --> 00:16:42.740
<i>Papa! Papa!</i>

301
00:16:42.740 --> 00:16:44.590
<font color="#ff00ff">(BREATHES HEAVILY)</font>

302
00:16:52.690 --> 00:16:54.350
<font color="#ff00ff">(LAUGHS)</font>

303
00:16:54.360 --> 00:16:56.490
<i>Papa! Papa!</i> It's him!

304
00:16:56.490 --> 00:16:58.360
I know who my
great-great-grandfather was.

305
00:16:58.360 --> 00:17:00.390
Miguel. get down
from there.

306
00:17:00.400 --> 00:17:03.160
<i>Mama</i> Coco's father
was Ernesto de la Cruz!

307
00:17:03.160 --> 00:17:04.460
What are you talking about?

308
00:17:04.470 --> 00:17:06.550
I'm gonna be a musician!

