00:17:09.570 --> 00:17:11.670
You keep secrets
from your own family?

311
00:17:11.670 --> 00:17:14.010
It's all that time
he spends in the plaza.

312
00:17:14.010 --> 00:17:15.410
Fills his head
with crazy fantasies.

313
00:17:15.410 --> 00:17:17.010
It's not a fantasy.

314
00:17:17.010 --> 00:17:19.280
That man was
Ernesto de la Cruz!

315
00:17:19.280 --> 00:17:21.150
The greatest musician
of all time!

316
00:17:21.150 --> 00:17:22.680
We've never known anything
about this man!

317
00:17:22.680 --> 00:17:26.420
But whoever he was. he still
abandoned his family.

318
00:17:26.420 --> 00:17:28.050
This is no future
for my son.

319
00:17:28.060 --> 00:17:30.590
But. <i>Papa.</i> you said
