324
00:17:39.040 --> 00:17:40.570
- If you would just let...
- Miguel...

325
00:17:40.570 --> 00:17:42.170
You will listen
to your family.

326
00:17:42.170 --> 00:17:43.470
No more music.

327
00:17:43.470 --> 00:17:46.620
