351
00:18:50.840 --> 00:18:52.560
I'll put you on the list.

352
00:18:54.780 --> 00:18:58.250
- Can I borrow your guitar?
- Sorry. <i>muchacho.</i>

353
00:18:58.250 --> 00:19:01.250
- You guys have a spare guitar?
- No.

354
00:19:01.250 --> 00:19:03.390
I need a guitar
